@startuml
actor User
participant GUI
participant GuiEventHandler
participant Semester
participant Course
participant Tag

User -> GUI : click "Add File"
GUI -> GuiEventHandler : pickfile()
GuiEventHandler --> GUI : selected file path

GUI -> GuiEventHandler : getTag(file)
GuiEventHandler --> GUI : tag name

GUI -> GuiEventHandler : pickpath(tag)
GuiEventHandler -> Semester : courses()
Semester --> GuiEventHandler : list of courses
GuiEventHandler -> Course : dept()
Course --> GuiEventHandler : Tag
GuiEventHandler -> Tag : name()
Tag --> GuiEventHandler : tag name
GuiEventHandler --> GUI : destination directory

GUI -> GuiEventHandler : savefileas(file, dir)
GuiEventHandler --> GUI : file saved

GUI --> User : show success message
@enduml
